{
  "stem": "6762.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why don't you come over to my house and make some coffee?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said, sure, why not?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Why don't you meet my friend?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That's my wife.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what's her name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or what was her name then?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ali.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She never changed her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We talk.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I came to her house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We lived in a small, a little small house called the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's by Holon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we talked, talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I kind of liked her, so I made up a date.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it started from there on, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I moved in-- my dad started communicating with me from America, maybe I want to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I managed, managed to get made some papers for me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I came here on December of '57, alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My wife couldn't come with me because the paper wasn't big enough collateral to come, my wife with my son, here.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I came by myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And a year later, when I established myself, my wife came with my little boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One wish is mine is that those things never happen again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I can say.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must tell-- I must say that I didn't say everything what I experienced because there's a lot of stuff that comes to your mind later, and I don't feel like going back, and going back, and going back.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many things.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was in trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was raped by natives there, all kind of stuff",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In, in, in, in Russia, in Asia there, by the native.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1942.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All kind of stuff what's--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To who?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Police?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People can't realize what does mean Russia, especially those days in a small town like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
